### 6. Module Cross-Connections

#### Provider Chain
```
App.tsx
  ↓
  AudioEngineProvider (wraps AudioEngineContext)
    ↓
    MediaPoolProvider (wraps MediaPool)
      ↓
      DawShell (main DAW UI)
```

#### Audio Engine Initialization Sequence
```
1. createAudioEngine() → AudioContext in suspended state
2. engine.resume() on user gesture
3. createMediaPool(engine.ctx, storage) → decode capability
4. createTransportClock(ctx, transportSAB) → playback control
5. createMixerEngine(ctx) → audio graph
6. createLookAheadScheduler(ctx, clock) → event scheduling
```

#### UI → Audio Control Flow
```
UI Actions (Zustand store actions)
  ↓
useDawStore.play() / setBpm() / etc.
  ↓
useAudioEngine() hook reads AudioEngineContext
  ↓
Transport/Mixer/Synth methods via direct API calls
```

#### Audio → UI Observation Flow
```
SharedArrayBuffer (metering, transport state)
  ↓
useTransportCursor() hook (reads transport SAB)
  ↓
UI re-renders with cursor, metering data
```

